label: "Scrapbook Documenting Clark's Life Complied by Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority"
description: Scrapbook pages made of pink construction paper with a decorative vine theme, leaves made of green construction paper. Media types include photographs, newspaper clippings, typescript pages, correspondence, and invitations. All dated material generated in the 1970s.
